        "created_at": "2012-03-07T22:47:31.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Happy Wednesday everyone!<br>\nI really didn\u2019t know what to open this evening so i closed my eyes ( after I was in my cellar) and blindly pulled out a 2005 Domaine Alfred Califa Pinot Noir.  Popped and poured.  Beautiful bouquet.  Th aroma fills the glass nicely.  Tasted bright very ripe cherries with a little tobacco on the finish. I thought this wine would have been over the hill but its quit pleasant.</p>\n<p>What bottle of wine did you open today?  Cheers!! <img src=\"/uploads/db3686/original/2X/0/0ff9bfcdb0964982cd3240b6159868fbdf215b1a.gif\" width=\"24\" height=\"18\" alt=\"[cheers.gif]\" title=\"cheers\"></p>",
