        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/m/ed655f/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2012-03-08T02:42:32.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>2009 Chateau Pezat on the rec of a fellow board member. Saw this locally and decided to buy it. Unfortunately not so good. Raisiny roasted flavors that I hope are not indicative of the vintage, since this is my first '09 BDX. Maybe a storage issue. Not undrinkable, and maybe some good fruit and some lightly floral elements, but flawed, either the bottle or the wine itself.</p>",
